Aim_egypt by razEr

This is an old map that begun as a (de) bomb defuse map, and which I slowly lost interest of. Revived it recently and decided to make it a aim map. 

Not completely happy about the result, but it's good enough for my shooting map ( not considering aim_skyfitaz then)


This map has HDR lighting. If your pc cannot handle HDR, simply remove it by typing mat_hdr_enabled 0 in console.


DAT IZ ALL!



I hope you guys enjoy this.
